{"tid":727702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國家安全考慮   特朗普政府拒絕中國移動進入美國市場","createTime":"2018-07-03T08:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T12:02:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf133e8ff272baf23ddec4bab9d26d3494bf07f2","tid":727702,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】中國移動在2011年向美國聯邦通信委員會（FCC）申請在境內提供電信服務，不過據外媒7月3日報道，特朗普政府拒絕中國移動進入美國電信市場，稱中國電信運營商會威脅到國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n據報，美國商務部下屬國家電信和信息管理局（NTIA）當地時間周一通過電子郵件發佈的一份文件顯示，美國聯邦通信委員會（FCC）將拒絕中國移動於2011提交的進入美國申請。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部所屬的國家電信暨資訊管理局（NTIA）最新聲明稿指出，針對中企「中國移動」擬進入美國電信市場的申請，他們認為中國移動的申請「將構成不可接受的國家安全和執法風險」。<strong>他們認為中國移動幕後的最大股東是中國政府。中國政府可以利用由中國移動建立的聯接，進行經濟間諜活動和情報收集。受影響的消費者可能包括固定和移動網絡運營商、電話卡公司和企業客戶。當中指中國移動「無可避免地會被中國政府利用、影響進而掌控」。</strong>文件還稱，中國移動曾表示該企業希望為美國和其他國家提供國際電話業務，無意在美國境內供應移動服務。美國政府行政部門建議FCC拒絕「中國移動」的申請。<br />\n<br />\nNTIA負責通信和信息事務的局長助理戴維&middot;雷德爾（David Redl）在一份新聞稿中表示，該機構官員與中國移動進行了「重要接觸」，但未能解決擔憂問題。FCC女發言人蒂娜&middot;佩爾基（Tina Pelkey）表示，該委員會將審查該文件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%BB%E5%8B%95%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-031900202.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-031900202.html&d=Hbpg4j%2F5NhQYtgRbQA9tJEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=066f49a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A7%BB%E5%8B%95%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-031900202.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52c13284daba18205177db744e42663ccb5d04a","tid":727702,"uid":106848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"侵侵真係做到嘢，又維護自身國家利益。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下做垃圾力架馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645957668f642b0c39367a61eb8fa1cd3c7efc76","tid":727702,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08150dfd9a2046df37af46c5d6c793bfda7dc7a7","tid":727702,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"__ __ __ __ __ __ __ __ 家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4079b1cebe0aaaecd02bdc8bdc363da97b5e0f67","tid":727702,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:02:38.000Z","msg":":<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}